snippet.textDisplay: What Xulfi bhai has created in this song is something out of this world. from lyrics to music and choosing the singers who did the justice with the whole message in this song. the set Oh my God.. the Animations artist. i mean creating something better than this would need heavenly intervention for sure. for me this song talks about the Tauheed concept. we all were created from a single particle of matter, be it plants, humans, planets or animals, the whole universe observable or the distant galaxies. In the essence and realm of existence all of us become one particle in quantum space and time. go forward or reverse, it starts from one and will end as one. we are just here temporarily, so why hate each other, why hurt each other. let's spread love. because eventually whatever way you choose, all the ways lead to the creator. so, choose the way of love, and one day enter into Heaven and meet him. i was crying in the end of the song with the love of Allah i have.
